Well, its' been forever since i've wrote in my l/j!

My weekend was wonderful...
 Thursday- spent time with Billy (5mth anniversary)
           Then went to Auburn to see Morgan with Marissa and Shannon!!
 Friday- slept in!! drove home from auburn
 Saturday- worked and helped Billy's family get ready to sell their house.
 Sunday- went to The Church at the Well ( I love it!) then went to Rojo's, then
         went to Billy's!
 Monday- my brother and i spent the day together!!
 School...
       it's going really great! i love all my classes!
       I can't believe it, i'm actually going to be a NURSE!! :)
I worked out for the first time in a while today! it felt great!

Billy and I are awesome, and everyday i love him more and more! thank goodness i found him. I don't know for sure, but when we started dating i might have messed things up for some people... if i did i'm sorry.  i'm glad though, that i did decide to go for it! I'm so happy with him!

Well this past week has been fun...

         * I went out to 41 with Billy, Lindsie, and Ryan
            -> the police came and the 17yr. old's were in trouble..(Billy)
         * Everyone went to Tiki Bobs and we had so much fun! Went to bed at 5
         * I woke up at 9, b/c my family came from Louisiana for New Years.
         * Billy came over to my parents crazy New Years party
         * I woke up sick, and i'm still sick!

I close friend of mind that i've been helping now believes in the Lord. Please pray for them to grow and develop a relationship with Christ.

*Remember* Christians walk by FAITH, not by SIGHT.

Billy, 
I Love You! I think you are the best, and i am so lucky to be with someone like you.  Since we first started dating i knew that you were someone special and unique. Every day I love you more and more. You are an awesome person and I would love to spend forever with you!

~Good Luck this semester for everyone!!~

My Christmas was fun.  we did things a little different this year: we normally go to Louisiana, and visit family.  But this year it was just my immediate family and we cooked a bunch of food and layed around the house all day watching movies.  

I woke up this morning at 1 o'clock; i was suppose to be at work at 1! So i've been here since about 1:15 and i wont be able to leave until 5 o'clock...BORING!!

I miss Billy! He's been in Hayleyville since Friday!! I Love him so much! I'm so lucky!

Well, I'm sitting in Jeff State's library waiting on Shannon to get done with her final....  (tick tock, tick tock).

My days have been slow. things will pick up i know. its getting close to CHRISTmas.

I took my math final yesterday, i guess i did alright, i dont wanna get my hope up though. i took my eng final today...piece of cake! (ha.ha.)  *Tomorrow is biology...(EEEK!)

I have a GREAT weekend ahead of me!.... i have to babysit friday night and saturday night!! oh well.. i need $$$$.

*I think i'm going to see ALEXANDER tomorrow with Billy!* :)   aw... i love him!  i wish that he could really see how much he means to me...i know i dont always show it but billy...I HONESTLY LOVE YOU!

Lord, give me strength to make it through some how... make me who you want me to be.

Who am I? That the LORD of all the earth...

would care light my way..

would care to feel my hurt...  who am i?

the eyes that see my sin, would look on me with love,

and watch me rise again, who am i?

i'm flower quickly fading, wave tossed in the ocean, i'm a vapor in the wind... still you hear me when i'm callin, LORD you catch me when i'm falling, and showed me who i am.... I AM YOURS!  who am i- Casting Crowns

Then i went and worked out, and bought stuff to make shannon's christmas present. then i went out to eat at Logan's for Bryan's birthday, then billy and i babysat Masie! I'm at work right now...and then at 1, billy and i are going christmas shopping!! that's so much fun, i can't wait!! i'm going to be super tired and stressed out next week, please pray for me to keep my head on straight next week. i've got finals, so more than likely i'm going to be up all night then go take my exam, then go home and sleep! i just can't wait until next weekend!! :)

- This is my first entry, and it starts out saying "HELP"!

   *Woke up late (as usual)       *Didn't have a ride to school because my car is in the shop.    *Finally woke Shannon up and she took me.    *Went to biology; freaked me out- FINAL IS next TUESDAY       *Went to math; BORING- final is next THURSDAY       *Studied for my LAB FINAL *1:00 went to LAB final *Grant and Ryan brought me home (no car)      *Billy came over after school; it felt so good to hold him, i missed him all day. its so weird how he's hurt me, but i still need him, and he still makes me get butterflies whenever he touches me, or even looks at me. We ate my dad's WONDERFUL spagetti, and things were going pretty good, but he had to go home :(      ->I'm about to go babysit at the Eldridge's house until about 8:30 (FUN!)       ->Maybe i'll get some studying done.            ****I feel bad cuz i never spend time with my family... I go to school then to work, then to billy's and then to shannon's....that's my schedule every day, and there's no time for my parents. They leave before i wake up, and they go to sleep before i get home. it really gets to me sometime, and its hard to not go to billy's cuz i'm completely crazy for him, and his family is AWESOME, and they're actually around whenever i'm there; they talk and spend time with each other and eat dinner together every night. My family goes out to eat almost every night; my uncle and aunt live with us; they do nothing but watch tv all night; and they're in bed by 9 or 9:30, b/c they have to get up at like 4:45 in the morning. I know that's no excuse to not spend some time with my family, but its just really hard, cuz my whole day is always stressful everyday, and Jesus is all i have during the day...its not like highschool where you have friends and teachers... so whenever i get off work i want someone there for me, and my family is always tucked and snoozin' whenever i get off.          *I am very blessed, and the LORD is amazing for the second chances and all the wonderful people he has put in my life. I thank him for everything. And i need him the most right now. Especially with finals coming up, cuz i'm just hangin in there, and these are going to make or break me.        *I also pray that Jesus will ease my mind from all these worries in my life: School; Family; Billy ;$$$$$ (need more of it)

Reminder: This is my life; I need to be who i wanna be!! Life is short, i only have this time to show this world why God brought me here!
